videos.description: Gorjok Gak grabs the offensive rebound off the missed shot from KeVaughn Allen and lays it back in.
videos.headline: Gators take advantage of second-chance points

videos.description: Egor Koulechov cuts through defenders in the paint and lays it in.
videos.headline: Florida's Koulechov drives to the basket for the layup

videos.description: Kevarrius Hayes gets the steal but misses the layup, Egor Koulechov is there with the putback tip-in.
videos.headline: Gators finish off fastbreak with tip-in shot

videos.description: Tanner Leissner splits two Florida defenders and finishes it off with a reverse layup.
videos.headline: New Hampshire's Leissner cuts through defenders

videos.description: Jordan Reed hits a 3-pointer at the end of the half tying the game at 32-32.
videos.headline: New Hampshire closes half with deep 3-pointer

videos.description: New Hampshire's John Ogwuche banks in the 3-pointer to take the lead but Jalen Hudson gives the lead back to Florida with a fastbreak dunk.
videos.headline: New Hampshire and Florida trade baskets
